  "texts": [
    "The STRATEGYQA dataset acts as a benchmark for reasoning-based Q&A.",
    "The necessary steps for models to respond are implicitly stated within the questions, and inference is carried out through the application of diverse strategies.",
    "It encompasses 2,790 samples, each consisting of a question focused on strategy, a breakdown of steps, and a paragraph providing evidence.",
    "• WIQA (Tandon et al, 2019).",
    "In particular, WIQA stands out as the inaugural dataset tailored for \"What if...\" queries pertaining to procedural reasoning."
  ],
